&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Facilitates EDD on customer accounts triggered by dollar value thresholds; and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
