&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;To be an ideal candidate a 3D Animator should be able to interpret concept art into its three-dimensional realization and create moving images using digital models via CGI software. They may be asked to create animation and special effects for film, television, video games, advertisements, websites, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Animation is the creation of a virtual world in which everything must be visualized and created from pure imagination. The 3D Animator brings an imagined universe and the characters that inhabit it to life. Everything within a frame has scope, weight and meaning. Animators need to be able to visualize new worlds into being.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
