&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Build for scale mindset: you approach problems with an eye to scale and automation, and keep up with developments in tech to continuously improve operational effectiveness and efficiency.&amp;nbsp; You understand applications of machine learning, and can work with our data scientists to frame and solve problems.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
