&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY AVA LABS?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re a world-class team of experts in computer science, economics, finance, and law with offices in New York City and Miami. We&#39;re passionate individuals creating a frictionless world by redefining the way people build and use finance applications. &lt;/span&gt;The company has received funding from Andreessen Horowitz, Initialized Capital, and Polychain Capital, with angel investments from Balaji Srinivasan and Naval Ravikant.&lt;/p&gt;
