&lt;li&gt;Our stack is progressive and open-source and includes Go, Rust, and TypeScript.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We spearhead ecosystem projects like &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar&quot;&gt;Lodestar&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ChainSafe/web3.js&quot;&gt;Web3.js&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ChainSafe/forest&quot;&gt;Forest&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ChainSafe/gossamer&quot;&gt;Gossamer&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We are global, remote-friendly, and open to contractors (who can commit to a minimum of 35 hours a week). For those local to Toronto, our casual, open-concept office in Chinatown has meeting rooms, lounge areas, and space to pull up a chair.&lt;/li&gt;
